{"tid":1432332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術修補]三個戰敗既原因&解決方法","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:59:38.000Z","uid":259613,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b92bcca88fe104241d8e1d5ddd17eded7afa35db","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一   膽小的前線</span></span></div><br />\n好多人full gear咁走上前線 但又其實好<span style=\"color: blue;\">細膽</span> D狗行前少少即刻向後跑<br />\n中後排既人見到就一定跟住<span style=\"color: blue;\">癲左咁跑</span> <br />\n遲早人踩人<br />\n前中排逼住一齊跑 成條<span style=\"color: red;\">防線散哂</span> <br />\n之後前排就落單比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解決方法</span></span><br />\n細膽既你可以試下企番中/後排<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上前線要有心理準備同速龍打</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">組隊 唔好單拖 </span><br />\nAlways Stick With Your Team. <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">走就一齊走 打就一齊打</span> ( 見<span style=\"color: red;\">二</span> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">1.5 空裝的你</div></span></span><br />\n冇<span style=\"color: red;\">泳鏡</span>豬咀既你幾勇都冇用 一放催淚彈 就重複<span style=\"color: red;\">一</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解決方法</span></span><br />\n快撚D買<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">二   比人打冇得還手</span></span></div><br />\n1.其實我地人數係<span style=\"color: navy;\">一定夠速龍打</span> <br />\n但次次一聽速龍 (狗毛都未見到條)<br />\n就走到亂哂 前排得番少少人(又重覆<span style=\"color: red;\">一</span>)<br />\n<br />\n2.大家都係得盾 <span style=\"color: red;\">冇武器</span><br />\n咁一定會驚(好多連盾都冇)<br />\n<br />\n3.係 唔一定要打 但退都可以退得好D<br />\n 前排退得夠定 速龍打都係打盾<br />\n (幻想下防暴個防線)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">同埋手足比狗捉冇人救</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解決方法</span></span><br />\n1 第一第二排應該要係長盾 (雙手)<br />\n退既時候 唔好散 一齊行 <br />\n(好似D防暴咁)<br />\n<br />\n2 另外有一班人 你地用短盾(單手) <br />\n請你地加番武器 <span style=\"color: red;\">左手盾右手棍</span> <br />\n鎚仔/<span style=\"color: gold;\">電筒</span>都好過冇 (D狗開始熄街燈)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有人比狗捉就沖番上前救人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3 <span style=\"color: red;\">唔好製做恐慌 </span><br />\n咪手要比心理準備中後排 <br />\n但唔好大叫:<span style=\"color: red;\">走呀</span> 試下叫:<span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚驚!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">前後排要互相信任</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2.5   永遠被動</span></span></div><br />\n次次都係班狗放TG/推進<br />\n我地先會有行動 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解決方法</span></span><br />\n 現場開會 <span style=\"color: red;\">攻其不備</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">三    兵力分配</span></span></div><br />\n1.兵種 <br />\n而家上得<span style=\"color: red;\">前線</span>90%都係<span style=\"color: red;\">消防兵</span> <br />\n長盾,短盾,弓兵,咪手...etc都完全唔夠人數<br />\n<br />\n2.地理<br />\nD狗都識係天台射9我地啦 點解我地唔得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.多D人組隊 <br />\n一TEAM人入面咩兵種都要有<br />\n就算係消防兵都要有盾同棍<br />\n<br />\n2.現場睇 咩兵種唔夠 就做<br />\n<br />\n3.多D去高位玩<span style=\"color: red;\">Angry Bird</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnM0hBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnM0hBn.jpg&h=70ef71e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n快D買<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/browse/c0-all-sports/c1-cross-training/c3-resistance-bands/_/N-1z1110o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fbrowse%2Fc0-all-sports%2Fc1-cross-training%2Fc3-resistance-bands%2F_%2FN-1z1110o&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7x5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=c7387498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/zh/browse/c0-all-sports/c1-cross-training/c3-resistance-bands/_/N-1z1110o</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">最後</div> <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">祝大家早日戰勝歸來</div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fb119f90dac41576d0f832f9959a928ea43dd4","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"097628e2be61596867c1db9f6205d878858adc5c","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee239e85515a9254773bb7d4307673a1431e4e0a","tid":1432332,"uid":142854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:13:12.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意玩波子棋...無論去到邊個國家都要玩<br />\n時時都要玩 唔玩唔得"},{"pid":"d21d85ffb907039a7a0d38e0aacbcf6571fe6398","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5c0086aec489701458cd8c13f4f7f304bd47236","tid":1432332,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101a6be0fb3afbb820d876db54c699fa8a4599a4","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:14:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6ae98ec867e2e5a9486a983705276c3e47c7b73","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"e9eb19beec2155682fd83dc8834d57082c8de0ff","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:17:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac924aaaf47c64a0067f07d74104b8261a11d6de","tid":1432332,"uid":259613,"lik